@startuml
!pragma teoz true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam DefaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam DefaultFontSize 12
title 图16  WebSocket 实时多人选座顺序图

actor "用户A 浏览器" as UA
actor "用户B 浏览器" as UB
participant "Nginx" as NGX
participant "SeatController (REST)\n/api/schedules/{id}" as Ctrl
participant "SeatService" as SVC
database "Redis 座位锁" as RDS
participant "STOMP Broker\n/topic/schedules/{id}/seats" as WS

UA -> NGX: 连接 /ws (WebSocket)
NGX -> WS: HTTP Upgrade
WS --> UA: STOMP CONNECTED
UA -> WS: SUBSCRIBE /topic/schedules/{id}/seats

UB -> NGX: 连接 /ws (WebSocket)
NGX -> WS: HTTP Upgrade
WS --> UB: STOMP CONNECTED
UB -> WS: SUBSCRIBE /topic/schedules/{id}/seats

== 用户A 锁座（REST，非 STOMP 上行）==
UA -> Ctrl: POST /api/schedules/{id}/seats/lock\n{seatIds:[A-12,A-13]}
Ctrl -> SVC: lockSeats(scheduleId, seatIds)
SVC -> RDS: SETNX encore:seat-lock:{id}:{seat}\n= userA, EX 900
RDS --> SVC: OK
SVC -> WS: publishSeatStatus(LOCKED, seatIds)
Ctrl --> UA: 200 锁定成功
WS ->> UA: {reason:LOCKED, seats:[...]}
WS ->> UB: {reason:LOCKED, seats:[...]}

note over UB
  用户B 屏幕上 A-12/A-13 即时变红(LOCKED)，
  无需刷新, 无需轮询。
end note

== 超时未支付 / 主动释放 ==
SVC -> RDS: 锁过期或 DEL（@Scheduled 5s 兜底）
SVC -> WS: publishSeatStatus(LOCK_EXPIRED, seatIds)
WS ->> UA: {reason:LOCK_EXPIRED, status:AVAILABLE}
WS ->> UB: {reason:LOCK_EXPIRED, status:AVAILABLE}

note over Ctrl, WS
  座位锁动作走 REST；服务端仅通过
  SeatStatusPublisher 单向广播到 /topic。
  区域票则广播 areas[]（AREA_LOCKED/SOLD/...）。
end note
@enduml
